name: Fons ex Incertum [act 2]
description:
My sound design exploration continues.

Try to do something different now. 
While the track still based on the patch that I made with Buchla Easel Command 208C, adding some glitchy beats from Qubit Nebulae v2 and some textures from Make Noise Morphagene made it richer and up to date.
Mixed and mastered in Cubase 11.

Music and artwork by Yaya Mando.
